cz.ive.location
Interface Jam

All Superinterfaces:
MoveAware, Updateable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DummyJamImpl, JamImpl
public interface Jam
extends MoveAware, Updateable

Interface for storing informations about movement of objects, to delay evaluation of reactions on this movement. It should also join movement messages as mentioned in the specification. So remove and add messages should be combined into one move message and so on.
